## **🛠️ 기술 스택**

### **📍프론트엔드**

- ㅋVue 3 + TypeScript + Pinia
- Vuetify 3
- Vue Router, Axios

### **📍백엔드**

- Node.js + Express
- MongoDB (Mongoose)
- JWT (or Keycloak)

### **📍DevOps**

- Docker / Docker Compose
- Kubernetes (K8s)
- Prometheus + Grafana
- GitHub Actions (CI/CD)

### **📍배포**

- AWS EC2 (또는 EKS, ECS)
- S3 + CloudFront (프론트 호스팅)
- MongoDB Atlas or AWS RDS

## **📈 시스템 아키텍처**

```
[Client(Vue)] --> [API(Node.js)] --> [MongoDB]
                             ↕
                    [Job Queue (BullMQ)]
                             ↕
               [AI Task Processor (Mock)]
```

---

## **⚙️ 인프라 구성도**

```
Docker Compose → Kubernetes → AWS EKS (또는 EC2)
       ↑                   ↑
 Vue + Node + Mongo     Prometheus + Grafana
```